data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bath brick ranch located close to everything in Monroe!  Home features huge updated kitchen, sun room with beautiful view of fenced in back yard, partially finished full basement, whole house generator and heated garage.  Home also has newer roof, newer picture window in living room, coved ceilings and hardwood floors in bedrooms.
